# 🌍 Wanderlust – Travel Booking Website

Welcome to **Wanderlust**, a beautiful, responsive frontend travel booking website.  
This project is designed to let users explore destinations, learn about services, sign up, and book trips with ease.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```plaintext
wanderlust/
├── css/
│   └── style.css
├── images/
│   └── (All images used in project)
├── index.html
├── about.html
├── signup.html
├── booking.html
├── destinations.html
└── README.md
```

---

## 📄 Pages Included

| Page                | Description                                  |
| ------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `index.html`        | Landing/Home page with Discover the World    |
| `about.html`        | About us section – our mission, team, values |
| `signup.html`       | Registration form for new users              |
| `booking.html`      | Form for booking a trip with user info       |
| `destinations.html` | Grid of popular travel locations .           |

---

## 🎨 Features & Tech Used

- HTML5 & CSS3
- Responsive Design (Media Queries, Flexbox/Grid)
- Stylish booking and sign-up forms
- Destination cards with hover animations
- Clean and modern UI
- CSS transitions, shadows, and border-radius
- Organized file structure

